        723.59,
        537.71,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p183_s0003",
      "text": "If the Preference bit (word 0, bit 22) is set to one by an Nx_Port, then it is requested that all frames",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        540.06,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p183_s0004",
      "text": "transmitted by the Nx_Port requesting this function be delivered according to the setting of the PREF",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        69.65,
        539.93,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p183_s0005",
      "text": "field in the CS_CTL field of the Frame_Header.  If this bit is set to one by the Fx_Port, the Fx_Port is",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        81.65,
        540.1,
        92.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p183_s0006",
      "text": "indicating that it shall deliver Class 2 and 3 frames transmitted by the requesting Nx_Port according",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        93.65,
        539.95,
        104.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p183_s0007",
      "text": "to the setting of the PREF field.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        105.64,
        234.41,
        116.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p183_s0008",
      "text": "NOTE 17 – An Fx_Port that responds with bit 22 set to zero may not itself support Preferred delivery, but other",
      "bbox": [
        105.0,
        129.85,
        539.99,
        139.9
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p183_s0009",
      "text": "Fabric Elements in the path to the destination may support it.  An Nx_Port may attempt Preferred delivery",
      "bbox": [
        105.0,
        140.83,
        540.03,
        150.88
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p183_s0010",
      "text": "even if the Fx_Port does not indicate support.",
      "bbox": [
        105.0,
        151.88,
        285.76,
        161.92
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p183_s0011",
      "text": "If this bit is set to one, the Fabric shall deliver both Data and Link_Control (class 2 only) frames ac-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.97,
        539.96,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p183_s0012",
      "text": "cording to the setting of the PREF field in the CS_CTL field of the frame header.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.97,
        449.25,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p183_s0013",
      "text": "The Preference bit is not meaningful for Class 1, and Class 6.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.97,
        368.15,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
